dc_title_s: Future Land Use Outagamie County, WI 2012
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents future land use for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2012.[This dataset contains the future land use information for Outagamie County. The future land use is projected to the year 2030.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
